OL,5, When her daughter's father was sent to 
OL,6, prison for child sexual abuse, Bethan  
OL,7, was horrified to discover he could     
OL,8, still be allowed access to their child 
OL,9, after he was released. It was a risk   
OL,10, she wasn't willing to take.            
OL,12,FOutside a Cardiff courtroom, a smartly 
OL,13,Fdressed young woman sits waiting,      
OL,14,Fanxiously. Bethan has never been inside
OL,15,Fa family court before, but she is here 
OL,16,Fto try to protect her child - whose    
OL,17,Ffather has been convicted of paedophile
OL,18,Foffences and is currently in jail.     
